Introduction

Lee Ah In is a South Korean singer. She was the Main Vocalist of the girl roup MOMOLAND.

She earned fourth place in the reality survival show "Finding Momoland", earning her a spot in the group. She debuted as a member of MOMOLAND on November 10, 2016 with their first mini album Welcome to Momoland. On February 14, 2023, MOMOLAND announced their offical disbandment.
